---
layout: base
title: Home
---
<div class="font-mono">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-terminal-accent">
    <span class="text-terminal-prompt">$</span> whoami
  </h1>
  <p class="mb-8 text-lg">
    A growth engineer that is constantly asking "why?" and then doing whatever is necessary to answer that question.
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-terminal-accent">
    <span class="text-terminal-prompt">$</span> ls recent-posts/
  </h2>
  <ul class="space-y-4">
    {% for post in collections.post | limit(3) %}
    <li class="border-l-2 border-terminal-prompt pl-4">
      <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="text-xl hover:underline">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
      <div class="text-sm opacity-70">{{ post.date | date("MMM d, yyyy") }}</div>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm">{{ post.data.description }}</p>
    </li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>
  
  <div class="mt-8">
    <a href="/blog/" class="text-terminal-accent hover:tui-inverse px-1 transition-colors duration-200">[View all posts â†’]</a>
  </div>
</div>
